    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Menu\nEASTERN",
      "Beverages\nCocktails\nBloody Mary\nScrewdriver\nVodka or Gin Martini\nBourbon\nLiquors\nCanadian\nVodka Gin • Rum\nScotch\nBeers\nSelected Brands\nLate Night Snack\nto be served anytime, at your request ...\nLiqueurs\nCourvoisier V.S.O.P.\nDrambuie\nKahlúa\nAmaretto di Saronno\nBailey's Irish Cream\nCointreau\nWines\nRobert Mondavi 1987 Woodbridge Cabernet Sauvignon\nRobert Mondavi 1988 Woodbridge Sauvignon Blanc\nBishop of Riesling 1987 Bereich Bernkastel Mosel\nDuc de Valmer Sparkling Wine\nAssorted Finger Sandwiches\nSliced Fruit\nCheese and Crackers\nVegetable Crudités\nFresh Fruit Salsa\nChocolate Truffles\nA variety of soft beverages are available including\nCoca Cola, Diet Coca Cola, Sprite,\nDiet Sprite, La Croix Mineral Water,\nMr. \u0026 Mrs.\nWake Up Service\nJust from the oven, warm and fragrant\nCinnamon Rolls\nMay we suggest one of our\nInternational Coffees\nCafe Mexicano = Kahlúa\nBailey's Irish Coffee = Bailey's Irish Cream\nCafe Royale = Courvoisier Cognac\nCafe Saronno = Amaretto di Saronno\nCafe Parisienne = Cointreau\nRoyal Scot Coffee = Drambuie\nA memento of your flight with our compliments.\nPrinted on 100% recycled and acid free paper\n6100/су 2/4"
    ],
